posting_body: ['**First full month free.', 'Prorated monthly rent after 1 month free is $1,409!', 'For a limited time you will also receive a $1000 Amex gift card and a reduced app & admin fee of $99.', 'Located in the Texas Hill Country famous for rolling hills and enormous star filled skies, is a beautiful and tranquil place to call home.', 'Next door to Austin Community College and just a short drive from the renowned Salt Lick Barbeque, this beautiful property is also just minutes to Downtown Austin via Hwy 290, Mopac & Wm.', 'Cannon.', 'The community features contemporary architecture, a serene pool with undisturbed green belt views, and extensive amenity spaces including a huge fenced dog park, so your furry friend will love calling it home just as much as you do!', 'This unit is outfitted with high-end finishes and appliances including Nest thermostats, granite counter tops and Decorative Pendant Lighting.', 'This property provides the best of both worlds -- enjoy wide open spaces at home with easy access to the fun and excitement of Downtown Austin!', 'Call/text Trent', 'to check it out today.', 'Trent Guerra', 'Apartment Locator + Sales Manager', 'Apartment Hunters LLC', '(8 1 7) 9 9 9-8 8 2 9', "** As a full-time apartment locator I will work day and night to help you find the perfect apartment here in the beautiful Austin Tx, my service is completely FREE to you so please don't hesitate and call me today!", 'Check out our Apartment Hunters Facebook and Google pages to see over one hundred 5 star reviews written from past clients and their experience with me!', '**']
